## Security Considerations
- Never hardcode secrets (client IDs excepted; no client secret in public/native flow)
- Validate user-provided file paths (avoid directory traversal if expanded)
- Handle large file streaming efficiently (current implementation loads directly)
- Consider audit logging for protection/revocation events

## Troubleshooting
| Issue | Possible Cause | Action |
|-------|----------------|-------|
| Authentication fails | Wrong ClientId / consent missing | Reconfigure AAD app & grant consent |
| No labels returned | MIP policies not published to user | Verify label publication in compliance center |
| Protection apply fails | User lacks rights / template misconfig | Check Azure RMS / AIP configuration |
| Revoke fails | Caller not Owner | Ensure Owner rights when protecting |

